></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531100\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531100\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 06, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pvq1665702696999.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvq1665702696999.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvq1665702696999.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pvq1665702696999\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n<samp class=\"ph msgph\">Mapping rule \"MappingRule\" for entity Entity.Model refers to output field FieldName, which is not known in the dictionary.</samp>\n</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvq1665702696999__p_d69119e1_d69120e1_d69121e1\">This message is generated when an XML export file is imported, and a target field specified in the mapping rules for the entity (in the mapping file <span class=\"ph filepath\">usysmap.dsc</span>), is not present in the entity’s signature.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvq1665702696999__section_ssb_m4g_tvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623252e67\"> Problem </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvq1665702696999__p_d69125e1_d69126e1_d69127e1\">This message may occur when the mapping file\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">usysmap.dsc</span> is not in sync with the signatures for the\n            Repository entities.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvq1665702696999__p_d69128e1_d69129e1_d69130e1\">Entity mapping rules defined in\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">usysmap.dsc</span> used by the import action may refer to target fields\n            that are not described in those entity signatures.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvq1665702696999__section_jfc_44g_tvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623252e85\"> Resolution </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvq1665702696999__p_d69134e1_d69135e1_d69136e1\">Ensure you are using the default descriptors and\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">usysmap.dsc</span> file provided by the Uniface installation.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531100\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531100\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Mapping rule \"MappingRule\" for entity Entity.Model refers to output field FieldName, which is not known in the dictionary. Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 06, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Mapping rule \"MappingRule\" for entity Entity.Model refers to output field FieldName, which is not known in the dictionary. This message is generated when an XML export file is imported, and a target field specified in the mapping rules for the entity (in the mapping file usysmap.dsc ), is not present in the entity’s signature. Problem This message may occur when the mapping file usysmap.dsc is not in sync with the signatures for the Repository entities. Entity mapping rules defined in usysmap.dsc used by the import action may refer to target fields that are not described in those entity signatures. Resolution Ensure you are using the default descriptors and usysmap.dsc file provided by the Uniface installation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}